00:31:47,542 --> 00:31:51,178
<i>Maybe I needed to prove to him</i>
<i>that I could handle this.</i>

326
00:31:51,211 --> 00:31:52,714
<i>Maybe I needed</i>
<i>to prove to myself</i>

