just let it pass.

352
00:33:53,801 --> 00:33:56,203
Um, adjust
the baby's position,

353
00:33:56,604 --> 00:33:59,072
maybe your own,
and resume feeding.

354
00:33:59,439 --> 00:34:02,309
Yeah, I-- I knew that,
I just, um...

