00:34:03,511 --> 00:34:04,612
I just forgot.

356
00:34:05,345 --> 00:34:06,413
Uh...

357
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:10,818
It just--
it all happened so fast,

358
00:34:10,852 --> 00:34:13,153
you know, like,
in that instant, it all--

359
00:34:13,186 --> 00:34:14,254
it all could've just--

